      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LITTLE DITZY (1) charged out of the boxes with a slick early split and went straight to the front, scoring an all the way win (15.82) over 275m at this track. Boasts three wins from three starts out of this box. Expected to go well again. RED HOT BERNIE (4) is overdue for a win after recording back to back placings, the latest jumping from this same box when a 3 length second (16.31) in a Free For All at this track. Harder here but will be in this for a long way. KABUKI WARRIORS (2) has a strong record this trip with two wins and two placings from five starts. Below best last time at Mandurah (23.02) in a Grade 5, finishing a 5 length fourth. Suited here and expected to run well. ZARA'S SECRET (3) was in the money last time at this track (16.25) in a Grade 4/5, finishing a 6 length third. Has already won two times from this draw.",
